      "title": "Over 11,000 Dengue cases in July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st): The Ministry of Health said the number of Dengue cases reported in 2022 is three times greater than the cases reported in previous years.",
        "Deputy Director General of Health Services Dr. G. Wijesuriya speaking to News 1st warned that Dengue is spreading rapidly among children.",
        "43,393 Dengue cases were reported so far in 2022, while 11,119 Dengue cases were recorded in July alone."
      ],
